metadata.name: EDITH : THE DEATHLY ANGELS NO.01
metadata.description:
THE 1st Angel
EDITH- THE WARLORD An angel who is blessed to win every war. from the saints. She specializes in all kinds of weapons and uses the Double-Edged Sword to fight demons. She is also the leader of the deathly angels.

THE DEATHLY ANGELS the deathly angels originated after the war of the heavens. The gods were victorious. and send the devil back to hell and formed a group of the deathly angels to guard the gates of hell. and chase away demons that have escaped.
